{
  "stem": "21527.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as the war went on, he became more and more corrupt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He used to take-- he wouldn't give us food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He used to take food and sell it on the black market because he was in charge of the food stores.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So unfortunately, even among our own people, there was some pretty horrible ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were acts of heroism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were people in the barracks who used to look after young girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were a lot of young girls, teenage girls or girls in there twenties.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the older women looked after them, and same with the men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was just unbelievable some of the acts of heroism have one covered for another case, in case one would be punished.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was some fairly orthodox people in the camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I don't know how because nobody had calendars, they used to work out with the Jewish festivals were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And to the extend that if you didn't eat bread, the other provisions were so meager, you really couldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But they used to work it out when it was Pesach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they used to swap bread for soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So they used to eat the soup and not eat bread for a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I think that in itself was heroic, because we were so undernourished and sickness was so rife that they could have died from malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But they just wouldn't eat bread over Pesach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My uncle-- as I said, my uncle used to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] buy newspapers, and my aunt used to stand guard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "If the Germans came, she used to give them a sign to hide the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we actually did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a nursing sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She'd been a nurse in Czestochowa for many years.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
